com.pingidentity.sdk

Interface GuiConfigDescriptorBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleGuiConfigDescriptorBuilder

    public interface GuiConfigDescriptorBuilder
    An interface that builds a GuiConfigDescriptor for a plugin descriptor. This interface offers different build methods for different situations.
    Since:
    6.11
    See Also:
    GuiConfigDescriptor, PluginDescriptor
